    "Not surprisingly, the U(2) 5 flavor symmetry has been discussed both in the context of supersymmetric models (see e.g.",
    "[4,7,8]), composite models (see e.g.",
    "[9][10][11]) and, more recently, in the framework of flavor non-universal gauge models (see e.g.",
    "[12][13][14][15][16][17]).",
    "The effective theory we are considering is therefore representative of a wide class of compelling NP models.Our analysis serves two primary objectives."
  ]
